mily: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">语法如下：</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p>Number<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>toLocaleString<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="st_h" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 145, 134); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&#39;en-US&#39;</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">举例：</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/>2<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="nu0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(174, 129, 255); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">123456789</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>toLocaleString<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="st_h" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 145, 134); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&#39;en-US&#39;</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span><br/>结果是：<span class="nu0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(174, 129, 255); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">123</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">,</span><span class="nu0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(174, 129, 255); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">456</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">,</span><span class="nu0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(174, 129, 255); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">789</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对于中文场景下，toLocaleString(&#39;en-US&#39;)中的&#39;en-US&#39;理论上是可以缺省的，也就是直接(123456789).toLocaleString()也是可以得到123,456,789。但是如果你的产品可能海外用户使用，则保险起见，还是保留&#39;en-US&#39;。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">另外，对于IE edge之前的版本，Number.toLocaleString()会自动补上两位小数，如果是不需要的，需要自己额外过滤掉。</p><p><br/></p>', 1512800573, 909, 'Public/Upload/default.png'),
(346, 'cc', '<p>\r\n    <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">锄禾日当午，<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0002.gif"/></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    汗滴禾下土。<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0006.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    谁知盘中餐，<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0004.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    粒粒皆辛苦。<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0002.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class="brush:css;toolbar:false"><br/></pre>\r\n<p>\r\n    div.mask{\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; position: fixed;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; width: 100%;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; height: 100%;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; top:0;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; left: 0;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; background-color: rgba(100,100,100,0.2);\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; div.mask&gt;div{\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; width: 800px;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; height: 300px;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; padding: 160px;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; margin: 150px auto;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; background: rgba(100,150,100,1);\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; font-size: 20px;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; box-sizing:content-box;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class="brush:as3;toolbar:false;"><br/></pre>\r\n<p>\r\n    <br/>\r\n</p>', 1515137614, 19, 'Public/Upload/default.png'),
(347, '11', '<p>\r\n    <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">锄禾日当午，<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0002.gif"/></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    汗滴禾下土。<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0006.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    谁知盘中餐，<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0004.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    粒粒皆辛苦。<img src="http://img.baidu.com/hi/jx2/j_0002.gif"/>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    <br/>\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class="brush:html;toolbar:false">div.mask{\r\nposition: fixed;\r\nwidth: 100%;\r\nheight: 100%;\r\ntop:0;\r\nleft: 0;\r\nbackground-color: rgba(100,100,100,0.2);\r\n}\r\ndiv.mask&gt;div{\r\nwidth: 800px;\r\nheight: 300px;\r\npadding: 160px;\r\nmargin: 150px auto;\r\nbackground: rgba(100,150,100,1);\r\nfont-size: 20px;\r\nbox-sizing:content-box;\r\n}</pre>\r\n<p>\r\n    <br/>\r\n</p>', 1515137754, 15, 'Public/Upload/default.png'),
