INSERT INTO `tb_news` (`id`, `title`, `text`, `date`, `browse`, `photos`) VALUES
(333, '巧用CSS3的calc()宽度计算做响应模式布局', '<p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">calc()从字面我们可以把他理解为一个函数function。其实calc是英文单词calculate(计算)的缩写，是css3的一个新增的功能，用来指定元素的长度。比如说，你可以使用calc()给元素的border、margin、pading、font-size和width等属性设置动态值。为何说是动态值呢?因为我们使用的表达式来得到的值。不过calc()最大的好处就是用在流体布局上，可以通过calc()计算得到元素的宽度。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box;">calc()能做什么？</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">calc()能让你给元素的做计算，你可以给一个div元素，使用百分比、em、px和rem单位值计算出其宽度或者高度，比如说“width:calc(50% + 2em)”，这样一来你就不用考虑元素DIV的宽度值到底是多少，而把这个烦人的任务交由浏览器去计算。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box;">calc()语法</strong><br/>calc()语法非常简单，就像我们小时候学加 （+）、减（-）、乘（*）、除（/）一样，使用数学表达式来表示：</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p>width<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">:</span>&nbsp;calc<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span>expression<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">其中”expression”是一个表达式，用来计算长度的表达式。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box;">calc()的运算规则</strong><br/>calc()使用通用的数学运算规则，但是也提供更智能的功能：</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1、使用“+”、“-”、“*” 和 “/”四则运算；</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、可以使用百分比、px、em、rem等单位；</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3、可以混合使用各种单位进行计算；</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4、表达式中有“+”和“-”时，其前后必须要有空格，如”widht: calc(12%+5em)”这种没有空格的写法是错误的；</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5、表达式中有“*”和“/”时，其前后可以没有空格，但建议留有空格。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box;">浏览器的兼容性</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171210/1512898451611107.png" alt="calc2"/></p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们来个例子，我们做一个三列并排的模块，宽度按百分比、有padding值、有border值、还有margin-right，而且这三个值是px，</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/>2<br/>3<br/>4<br/>5<br/>6<br/>7<br/>8<br/>9<br/>10<br/>11<br/>12<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p>li<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">{</span><br/>float<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">:</span>left<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span><br/><br/>width<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">:</span><span class="nu19" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 110, 117); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">33.3333</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">%;</span><br/>height<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4e