argin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">else</span>&nbsp;<span class="kw1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">if</span>&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>permission&nbsp;<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">!=</span>&nbsp;<span class="st0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 145, 134); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&quot;denied&quot;</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span>&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">{</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>requestPermission<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="kw2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">function</span>&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span>permission<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span>&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">{</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; popNotice<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">}</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">}</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">}</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; desktop<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">}</span>&nbsp;<span class="co1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 110, 117); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">// else {</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="co1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 110, 117); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">// &nbsp; &nbsp; alert(&#39;浏览器不支持Notification&#39;); &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br/>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="co1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 110, 117); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">// }</span><br/><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">}</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">,</span><span class="nu0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(174, 129, 255); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">10000</span><span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">;</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><h4 class="h4" style="margin: 15px -15px; padding: 8px 15px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left: 4px solid rgb(255, 174, 91); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(255, 174, 91); background: rgb(251, 251, 251); font-weight: normal; white-space: normal;">兼容性</h4><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171211/1512963364202856.png" alt="" width="788" height="220" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-991"/></p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">注：Notification目前还未标准化，且必须在环境下才能运行，直接本地html无法运行</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">使用Notification的流程</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">这些属性仅在 Notification 的实例中有效。</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/>2<br/>3<br/>4<br/>5<br/>6<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>title 只读&nbsp;<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">(</span>moz only<span class="br0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(251, 31, 93); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">)</span>&nbsp;在构造方法中指定的 title 参数。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span><a href="http://www.php.net/dir" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><span class="kw3" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 20, 147); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">dir</span></a>&nbsp;只读 通知的文本显示方向。在构造方法的 options 中指定。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>lang 只读 通知的语言。在构造方法的 options 中指定。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>body 只读 通知的文本内容。在构造方法的 options 中指定。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>tag 只读 通知的 ID。在构造方法的 options 中指定。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>icon 只读 通知的图标图片的 URL 地址。在构造方法的 options 中指定</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">事件处理</p><table width="788"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/>2<br/>3<br/>4<br/>5<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>onclick&nbsp;<br/>处理 click 事件的处理。每当用户点击通知时被触发。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>onshow 处理 show 事件的处理。当通知显示的时候被触发。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>onerror 处理 error 事件的处理。每当通知遇到错误时被触发。<br/>Notification<span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span>onclose 处理 close 事件的处理。当用户关闭通知时被触发。</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">移动端要是支持的话，我猜，可能会跟原生app的提示效果类似，直接出现在屏幕上，感觉到时候应该蛮吊！本文来自<a href="http://www.zhangxinxu.com/wordpress/2016/07/know-html5-web-notification/" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 136, 204); text-decoration-line: none;">简单了解HTML5中的Web Notification桌面通知</a></p><p><br/></p>', 1512963415, 1312347, './Public/Upload/2017-12-11/5a2dfd575229d.png');
INSERT INTO `tb_news` (`id`, `title`, `text`, `date`, `browse`, `photos`) VALUES
(338, '未知高度和宽度元素的水平垂直居中 （不外传秘法）', '<p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">在说到这个问题的时候，我们都知道，table默认文字就是垂直居中显示的，也许有人会问Div中CSS中不是有text-align属性来设置垂直居中的吗？是的，通常我们使文字垂直居中用的就是这个属性，但是在正式开发时候单单掌握这个可不够，例如：现在有一需求，在div中（固定宽高），里面内容不固定，不管是文字占1行还是多行都在div中垂直居中，那么应该怎么做？</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">当要被居中的元素是inline（例如span）或者inline-block（例如div/p）的时候，可以巧妙的将父级容器设置为display:table-cell，配合text-align:center和vertical-align:middle即可以实现水平垂直居中。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/ueditor/php/upload/image/20171211/1512995231444884.png" alt="" width="782" height="417" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671"/></p><table width="1627" style="width: 992px;"><tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" class="firstRow"><td class="line-numbers" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;" width="20"><p>1<br/>2<br/>3<br/>4<br/>5<br/>6<br/>7<br/>8<br/>9<br/>10<br/>11<br/>12<br/>13<br/>14<br/>15<br/>16<br/>17<br/>18<br/>19<br/>20<br/>21<br/>22<br/>23<br/>24<br/>25<br/>26<br/>27<br/>28<br/>29<br/>30<br/>31<br/>32<br/>33<br/>34<br/>35<br/>36<br/>37<br/>38<br/></p></td><td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;"><p><span class="sy0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 38, 89); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&lt;!</span>DOCTYPE html&nbsp;<span class="kw2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">PUBLIC</span>&nbsp;<span class="st0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 145, 134); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot;</span>&nbsp;<span class="st0" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 145, 134); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1.4em;">&quot;http://www.w3.or