(339, '关于事件mouseover ,mouseout ,mouseenter,mouseleave的区别', '<h4 class="h4" style="margin: 15px -15px; padding: 8px 15px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left: 4px solid rgb(185, 211, 41); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(185, 211, 41); background: rgb(251, 251, 251); font-weight: normal; white-space: normal;">定义和用法</h4><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">当鼠标指针离开元素时，会发生 mouseleave 事件。<br/>该事件大多数时候会与 mouseenter 事件一起使用。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">mouseleave() 方法触发 mouseleave 事件，或规定当发生 mouseleave 事件时运行的函数。</p><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">注释：与 mouseout 事件不同，只有在鼠标指针离开被选元素时，才会触发 mouseleave 事件。如果鼠标指针离开任何子元素，同样会触发 mouseout 事件。请看下面例子的演示。</p><h4 class="h4" style="margin: 15px -15px; padding: 8px 15px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); border-left: 4px solid rgb(255, 174, 91); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(255, 174, 91); background: rgb(251, 251, 251); font-weight: normal; white-space: normal;">关于mouseover ,mouseout ,mouseenter,mouseleave冒泡机制问题</h4><p style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; list-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">通过测试我发现，mouseover ,mouseout子元素上移动时候触发父元素事件，但并不是冒泡产生的，也就是说禁止冒泡没任何效果，而mouseenter,mouseleave则支持冒泡，但是它的冒泡事件会和通常我们所想的不同，并不会由子元素触发冒泡</p><p><br/></p>', 1513038231, 134, './Public/Upload/2017-12-12/5a2f2197adfa5.png');

